Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.10,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Coming right up!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has classic features.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,《目鼻立ちは　整ってて\N背も低からず　高からず》
